Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:08.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone, for your \Nsupport of {\i1}Magic Kaito{\i0} last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:11.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now then, ladies and gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:26.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Best wishes for a...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:32.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please keep watching this year, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:02.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:03.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:12.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:14.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:17.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Would you knock it off, already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How many times have you \Ncrashed into me today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:22.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:24.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a beginner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then ski over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why'd you even come?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:39.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?! I'm trying my best here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:47.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Whoop it up while you still can,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kuroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:53.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the day you become my captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:58.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But still, Aoko Nakamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:01:59.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...is a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.51,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Get Away From Him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,Welcome\NEveryone from Egota High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:52.14,Signs,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You have half a day left to ski.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A fun event awaits you this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A "fun event"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nobody said anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a masquerade ski tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You find a partner and \Nski together as a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sensei, can't girls partner with girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:17.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When I say "couple," I mean a boy and a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:22.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On the slope at twilight, \Nmaking trails side by side...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:25.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In your own little world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Konno-sensei, did you eat a \Nmushroom you found on the slope?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shush. You can't interrupt \Nat a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:36.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right. Girls hold on to an innocent \Nromantic streak, no matter how old they get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cold snow all around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:47.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But the light of love that flares up \Nbetween the two of you melts it all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:47.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,Snow White Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:51.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I understand, but you can be \Nromantic without being delusional!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:55.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I admit she is \Ngoing a little too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:05:00.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling Konno-sensei was \Nreally lonely in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:03.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bet this will be the first page \Nin the springtime of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I came up \Nwith this brilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's with the "masquerade" bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just skiing is no fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:22.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course I've prepared a delightful \Npresent for the best couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:24.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now she's talkin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! We get a prize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:31.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You might want to spend some time \Nworking on your costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and that's all I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard the hot spring here is co-ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like I'm gonna pair up with a \Ncrappy skier like you, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nakamori-san, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:15.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nakamori-san, you've got a \Ncrush on Kuroba-kun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:18.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-Not especially!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:30.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuroba-kun isn't the \Nsimpleton you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's more mysterious, more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:39.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The point is, he isn't a good \Nmatch for your mediocrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why don't we make a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:48.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Which of us will he pair up with for this \Nevening's masquerade ski tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Whoever loses has to keep away from...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-Nakamori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, it's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:59.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A beautiful girl like you \Nwith a crush on Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out why he's so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what do you like about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's {\i1}on{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:20.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-chan is cute when she blushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:25.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. So she likes Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I envy Akako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She can ski with Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fujie-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:59.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fujie-kun, you like Akako-chan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She sure is a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I don't stand a chance with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a fat wallflower who can't ski.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-sama can only be \Nthe girl of my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:17.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In fact, I doubt there's \Nanyone out there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:20.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's... That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why don't we ski together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're both lousy, but let's \Ndo our best. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But what about Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be with Aka... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll pair up with a good skier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're as good as ever, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Eat my dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:13.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kuroba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hi, Akako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a wonderful skier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This girl rubs me the wrong way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wiped out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see you're as uncoordinated as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:48.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,By the way, you haven't decided yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Decided what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:53.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You know, for that pair \Ntournament thing this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you out in the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So I'll pair up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:04.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, I heard that Nakamori-san \Nis going to be with Fujie-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Aoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:12.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I guess that's out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The lift's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you later, Nakamori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:34.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? You've been \Nsulking since we got on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You will pair up with me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look! This ski outfit is cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Say, Kuroba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:11:00.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Getting caught up with that girl would ruin \Neven Kid the Phantom Thief's reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:08.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We could always pair up for good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this girl serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll be partners, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:21.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems the heart sticker \NI slapped on his back is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:27.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a charm that makes the person \Nyou put it on be your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you'll be mine, heart and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This girl's got a screw loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just sitting around...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nobody else is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's great! Like it's reserved for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But this is a mixed hot spring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When I checked before, it was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:09.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko, I see you're still \Nflat as two pancakes up top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:14.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}A-Aoko! Th-This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:16.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it! A lot of guys \Nactually have a flat chest fetish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:17.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:21.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, somebody's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think you mean me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How cute! A husky voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:33.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just got an eyeful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, why \Ndidn't you and Kaito pair up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, after all, I'm terrible at skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito hates being around incompetent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:01.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If we skied together, I'd only embarrass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito is always clowning around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So as his childhood friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:13.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I want to make him look cool once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So this way is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It ain't fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Does it look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I'm sure Aoko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:54.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid and Inspector Nakamori \Nare gonna win for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyuk nyuk nyuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how your Dad laughs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:58.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like you would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaito-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:03.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cute sticker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Akako must've stuck it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-sama's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've got a thing for Akako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:22.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:22.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:36.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone, line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kannou-san is into it more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though she doesn't ski herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:51.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,Asuka Barber\NA-1 Women's Club\NYuhi Liquor Store\NMato Orthopedic Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:48.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The judges of this masquerade \Nski tournament are
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:51.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,local merchants I found \Nwalking around town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:54.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed she snagged them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What kind of costume is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your ribbon is crooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll think I'm gay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She's impressive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:04.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:09.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now, let's begin the \Nmasquerade ski tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Entry number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Polar Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not enough tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,3, 1, 3, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's 9 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next up, entry number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The One-inch Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:37.26,Signs,,0,0,0,,Asuka Barber\NA-1 Women's Club\NYuhi Liquor Store\NMato Orthopedic Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The bowl overturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, only 5 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Entry number three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Astronauts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Town Musicians of Bremen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Titanic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikkyu-san and the Folding Screen Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Masked Yaiba and Laser Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Alice Through the Looking-Glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:14.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where did Fujie-kun go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nakamori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Entry number 83!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Snow Queen and the Abominable Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:48.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kuroba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:57.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Observe our magnificent skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:15.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,10, 10, 9, 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,An impressive 39 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:25.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This could be our winning duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:32.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I mean, for being an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where's Fujie-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's with the object of \Nhis affection, Akako-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:55.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We got an amazing score, Kuroba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Akako-sama and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But can't you do something \Nabout that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...do something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, you're like the real Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:26.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dumbass! I'm cooler than the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:30.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But what are we gonna do? I can't ski.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:38.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:44.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Entry number 84! Kid the Phantom Thief \Nand Princess Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Kaito Kuroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's dressed up as his alter ego...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That boy knows no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-Then who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:27.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,10, 10, 10, 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A perfect 40 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:29.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The winners, from class 2-B, \NKaito Kuroba and Aoko Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You really are clumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:37.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:41.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never be able to catch me like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He did it to me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here's your souvenir from the ski lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:12.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,Winning Prize\NMasquerade Ski Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:12.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:22.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Winning Prize\NMasquerade Ski Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:30.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In a winter wonderland, a witch used \Na spell to bind people's hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:35.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,while an illusionist presented \Nidentity-switching magic tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:39.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But was the illusionist who made \Na deep impression on the girl
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:42.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,under the moonlight\N real or an impostor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:47.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:22.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I let Aoko narrate last episode's preview,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.30,0:23:24.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but she did a terrible job!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've really gotta do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:28.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So the next setting is aboard a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:32.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm after a queen's jewel, \Nbut she's a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:36.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And her son, the prince, \Nis pretty sharp for a squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:38.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He reminds me of someone else I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NCrystal Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,Crystal Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:45.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:47.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
